adjunction $(-)^{\freshfor a+} \dashv \delta_a^+ : \mathbf{FMLin}_s
\leftrightarrows \mathbf{FMLin}_{s\udot\{a\}}$ to a corresponding adjunction on
the coKleisli categories of the respective $!$ comonads.

